{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC13_ODI_610.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x22,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x117,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, I know this is sudden,<CR>but I am very bored."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x119,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, you should come visit this place more often."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "So you're bored? Now that I think about it, what do you usually do, Ms. Odelia?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I do nothing. If you must know,<CR>I am on standby."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Oh, standby?<CR>That sounds hard...I think?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Yes. Over what seems like an endless passage of time, I continue to wait for my next order..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "It is very hard and boring.<CR>However, those are my orders."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "The rental of books and the work that is in conjunction with that were originally 50% of my duties."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Keeping and maintaining this facility was 40%, and 10% was maintaining myself..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x117,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "However, no one has visited this facility for a long time, and excluding the 10% for my self-maintenance..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x118,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "The remainder of my 90% is spent on standby."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x119,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "The straightforward explanation<CR>is that I simply do nothing from<CR>morning till night."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I see. Doing nothing...<CR>That must be hard..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "XXX"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Th-Then, maybe you should read a book... Since you are in a library..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x198,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "My brain is directly connected with the library. There is no need for me to read the books."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Th-Then, take a nap or eat meals..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, I have no need for meals."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I do not require sleep, either."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Huh!? That's no good! Ms. Odelia,<CR>eating and sleeping are the basics<CR>for living a healthy life."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I know! I'll bring something tasty next time! Is there anything you like to eat?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x14e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I told you that I do not need food. Ayesha, you do not seem to listen to what other people are talking about."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x150,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "However, speaking of food...I feel like I do have an old memory..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Master, what is this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x3a,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "This? This is something I have prepared for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x3a,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It's been exactly one year since you were born, so it's a present for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x3a,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "See? It smells sweet, doesn't it?<CR>Now, go ahead and open it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x3a,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Today might be the last day I'll ever get to spend with you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Master, thank you. Hehehe, I wonder what it is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Well then...maybe I would like to eat something sweet."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "I cannot recall from such an old<CR>memory, but I feel as though it<CR>was very fascinating..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "I have heard that sweet love is something that exists. I would like to taste that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "I-I don't know about the love part,<CR>but I can bring you some sweets."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Anyways, let's try eating some together! I'll make something sweet and bring it next time!"
        }
    ]
}